Since People will ask for Pics & stuff about it. Here you go newbs.
Now, It is Deltascape, Just Moved a round a Little, Turned once again into a Pk server. I have fixed and added a few things.
- Fixed Dragon Fireshield - [url=http://tinypic.com/player.php?v=f54lj7&s=4]http://tinypic.com/player.php?v=f54lj7&s=4[/url]
- Added Black Mask - Added better Kbd - Added more realistic DFS Spec. - Added Mith dragons - Fixed rune C'bow a little. - Added GodWars - Added More Shops - Xp rate at about 6K, which in deltascape, its about 700 Xp in a normal Server Why?: Because deltascape doesn't hit very high, When low Str, 1 - 4, So I calculated and its kinda like 700 Xp rate in a normal Server. - Took out Barrows Mini game, Why?: Unrealistic and I fucked it up a little. Lol. I added a Barrrows Shop And Made a ::fix command. - Added more items in the Assault Shops - Took Out all Quest and requirements for weapons. [ Pk Server Duh. ] - Fixed the Neitz Helm, Dragon Scimi, DDS log out and In glitch. [ IDK why it was there lol. ]
Again It is Deltascape, If you don't know what features it has, Go look it up.
Now, Here are Some Pictures and videos about the server. I really don't feel like writing More. :S
